Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驱同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:02:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊呀 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}给你倒杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}吵醒你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我一直在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}还有些没睡醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}从前有部电影里说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}豆蔻年华的女孩子趴着睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就证明她坠入了爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我倒是觉得为人父母
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就算不看这种地方也会马上知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不会有事先知道结局的爱情片的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你已经知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不…没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是知道了会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这种恋爱会很无聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我不太懂透子说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过要是真能预知未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就可以享受两次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}妈妈 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就算知道未来是痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也能事先做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}尽是好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}能享受两次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说不定很美妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}如果能做出好作品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就可以再体会一次那种感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}如果是恋爱的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}如果是恋爱的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一条虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}虫子么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是什么虫子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我们家的女儿虽然是个乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但毕竟正值豆蔻年华呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}豆蔻？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 透子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是冲仓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}现在方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}上次 到最后你也没说有什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.61,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我再打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}挂掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一下子就被挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是上次的那个女孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我去冲咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你没做什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}经历两回初吻这种 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}做不到 做不到 做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}心脏要炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}冲仓同学 刚才不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不好意思 我是祐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}话说 今天的集会上…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我有些事情想跟你聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦 你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今后怎么能一直保持这种心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}该怎么去见她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早上好 大懒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}妈妈叫我们吃饭 你没听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…我刚才在换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:06:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早饭要凉了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天去风道之前 我有些事要办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}其实我只请透子先来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你去了小幸家的事我已经听她说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸可能对祐有兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是或许太害羞了不敢直接说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是…是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是请不要告诉雪哉和柳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 大家都知…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}因为我想亲口跟他们说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 嗯 也是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:07.78,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天也真热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我已经告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}了不起 小柳好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我挺喜欢透子你那感觉良好又少根筋的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.01,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}最近怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.50,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我讨厌热天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:31.28,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那我就开门见山地说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}幸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没错 这次的主角就是小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是想给她个惊喜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}之前的烟花大会她不是没去成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以我想办一场小幸也能参加的烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你们不这么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}赞成 真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}通过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}虽然总觉得作为考生 我们最近活动太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那我去跟小幸说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明明在这里接就可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是没法在这接的电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}谁打来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是大卫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么 要是知道他的联络方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就把他也请来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是说让透子邀请他？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 那我来邀请他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我来请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我知道他家在哪 大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以说为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我们刚才正在讨论要不要邀请大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}顺水推舟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}您好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是井美 冲仓同学的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你竟然知道我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}冲仓家在这附近很有名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你有时间的话 我想去外面说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我真是个名副其实的大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 这里是冲仓家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个 我是深水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}冲…驱同学在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驱出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}井美同学也是你的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 算吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}其实我根本就不想叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那不叫我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}世上的事情可不能简单地由主观愿望决定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我们要办一场烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我来邀请你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}虽然你不想叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是又有不得不叫我的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没必要专程去兴风作浪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}自你来了之后我们这就风波不断了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你是故意的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你很开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么可能开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那不是我的主要目的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和你一样 我不是想做才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这是什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你和透子的关系算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你没注意到透子的心意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子什么都没跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}而且我也没必要和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}高山向你告白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你不会是还没有回复她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这次还是别叫驱同学了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你脸怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}总之很疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}难道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}难道 难道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是被小雪打的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是我说重了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}高山似乎向他表明了自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是不是对小雪做了很过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}其实最近好多事情我都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大家一起凑钱买的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}线香烟花 我很喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}太好了 买了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么说也是给小幸办的烟花大会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}本来是惊喜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你的心意我已经感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欢迎回…来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那家伙不来烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}发生什么了 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}两个男人争抢透子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我到底算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我不是让你道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我知道不能这样一直下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我爸爸也在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:10.82,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}讨厌 这里全是我的CD嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.25,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嘛 我是你的粉丝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:14.45,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}让我为你弹一曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.44,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好呀 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我妈妈来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我今天先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你妈妈是那个钢琴家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一来这里我就能安静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你妈妈是什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她呀 是个不会停在一个地方的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不知道是由于职业还是由于性格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是个活泼的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小时候 不管妈妈做什么我都觉得是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}该说是恋母情结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也有这么想的时候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我都打了两次电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子要说的那件事 差不多该告诉我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}两次都没有说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸说要住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}虽然小幸说是住院检查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要我别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是我看到了她住院的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你很担心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉 透子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我有件不得不跟你说的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是打了冲仓同学的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你见过他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}现在我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}到校园里来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我们把话说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子是站在我这边的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快去阻止小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}他们要见到的话一定会不得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}突然打了你 我向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是你真觉得对不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就和我来场比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}正好这里有合适的场地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}跑步？ 你跟我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}能让你认真起来的就只有跑步了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你赢了 我就不会再见透子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我赢了 透子就是我的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你还有高山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}故意输给我也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}反正你根本就没想跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我不知道你的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是你选择的做法最差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}别去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 烟花大会要延期了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是大卫同学没有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要不我们先来一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳说的是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我没准备跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不想跑的我是不可能赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}发展成两个人相争 我究竟是想怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}自己也不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这么说好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这种话什么也说明不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}总之我也许是希望听到透子说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}「我是站在驱那边的」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子是怎么看「未来的碎片」的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}能…能享受两次 和心理准备？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你真的很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}之所以命名它为「未来的碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是因为我把它当成了自己缺少的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不完整的我变成稳定形态时需要的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是那些碎片只是些微小的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}或是人们的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不再有其他的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}见到透子之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我渐渐懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我真正想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不是那些莫名其妙的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是更清楚 更具象的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我听到的 全是你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我看到的 也全是驱同学的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…找到了吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================NEXT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我讨厌大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}未来是无法改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我和驱同学算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我今天先回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个 请不要这么逊
